<div id="descriptionContainer">
  
      <div id="description" class="readable stacked" style="right:0">
        
<span id="freeTextContainer4477909043403669335">In <i>Greenmantle</i>, Richard Hannay, hero of <i>The Thirty-Nine Steps</i>, travels across war-torn Europe in search of a German plot and an Islamic Messiah. He is joined by three more of Buchan&apos;s heroes: Peter Pienaar, the old Boer Scout; John S. Blenkiron, the American determined to fight the Kaiser; and Sandy Arbuthnot. Greenmantle himself is partly modeled on Lawrence of Arabia. Th</span>
  <span id="freeText4477909043403669335" style="display:none">In <i>Greenmantle</i>, Richard Hannay, hero of <i>The Thirty-Nine Steps</i>, travels across war-torn Europe in search of a German plot and an Islamic Messiah. He is joined by three more of Buchan's heroes: Peter Pienaar, the old Boer Scout; John S. Blenkiron, the American determined to fight the Kaiser; and Sandy Arbuthnot. Greenmantle himself is partly modeled on Lawrence of Arabia. The intrepid four move in disguise through Germany to Constantinople and the Russian border to face their enemies-the grotesque Stumm and the evil beauty of Hilda von Einem.</span>
  <a data-text-id="4477909043403669335" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

