<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Jake, our spy Hannah has played parts all along, he likes to 'hide in plain sight." I THINK, at the end, he and his buddies, including Sandy, haven't <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Jake, our spy Hannah has played parts all along, he likes to 'hide in plain sight." I THINK, at the end, he and his buddies, including Sandy, haven't let go of all identities. The Great Prophet ??? and the four next in line ??? appear to be dead, and successor has been appointed. They don't know yet who it is, but I think they are leaning toward the possibility that no one is Rising Up in the East at all. ??? I'd think in the next one, we learn all, but it wouldn't surprise me if Hannah poses as this next sucessor just to scare Germans.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
